ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: Upload any docs to "Original Docs" and then select "Manage Assignments" to assign subordinates or "Hand-Off" button to forward to a releasing authority.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: Review the Task instructions and associated documents in the "Original documents" library and then either "Accept" or "Reject" the Task.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: Enter your response into the My Response tab, upload documents to the appropriate library, Save and Complete tasker OR select "Manage Assignments" to task others.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: Your task is assigned to a subordinate OPR and has not been completed. You have the option of canceling their assignment from "Manage Assignment" or waiting for their completion.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: The assigned OPR has completed the task and it is ready for your review. View the "My Response section" to see the proposed response. When necessary, you can reopen the task for additional action.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: Your task is assigned to a subordinate OCR and has not yet been completed. You have the option of canceling their assignment from "Manage Assignment" or waiting for their completion.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: Subordinate assigned OCR(s) have completed the task and it is ready for your review. View "Consolidated OCR Coord" to see the response(s). When necessary, you can "Reopen" their task for additional action.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: This task has been reopened for additional action/review. Complete the necessary actions to review and complete or contact the assigner as necessary.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: The response to this task has been routed for approval. Click on "Tasker Status" to review the status of the approval route participants.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: The coordination Approval Route for the task has been completed. You can review the Approval Route and review comments from Tasker Status. Take any necessary actions prescribed by approval authorities or select "Close" to move this task to an inactive status.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: The approval route has been canceled.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: The prepared response this this task has been disapproved by a reviewing authority. Review their comments and take the appropriate action.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: This task has been completed. Ensure all response actions have been completed and then select "Close" to move change the state of the task to inactive

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: This tasker was completed prior to your response being submitted. Contact the assigner if you have questions.

ElementValue.Name: DefaultText
ElementValue.Value: This task has been cancelled. No additional action is required.
